long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The collaboration plugin bringing Analytics and Business Operations closer together.

The plugin has bi-directional sync with Slack, built-in Jira integration, dashboard annotation, task management, and more. Paradime Synq currently works with Looker and Tableau dashboards, and we will soon announce more integration options.

Now all your dashboard troubles can be managed with zero context switching. You only need a free Paradime account to get started.
